snippet.title: Lego Pirates of the Caribbean DS 100% Guide Part 1: Movie 1 Level 1 Port Royal [ALL MINIKITS]
snippet.description:
Part 1 of my 100% walkthrough of LEGO Pirates of the Caribbean on the Nintendo DS.

LEGO Pirates of the Caribbean is a casual adventure game where the goal is to accomplish certain objectives in different levels while collecting "studs" to gain a score. In this series, I will show how to get all of the collectibles in each level of this game including all Minikits, Character Tokens, and Red Bricks.

I did not livestream this game, but I also have a streaming account called WKStreams: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgIR0tL5e0TdPlnBWmI0TYw
